%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Battle%20For%20Rs%2011%2C000%20Crore%20Tobacco%20Empire%2C%20Son%20Accuses%20Mother%20Of%20Assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESamir%20Modi%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Godfrey%20Phillips%2C%20has%20accused%20his%20mother%20of%20orchestrating%20an%20attack%20on%20him%2C%20an%20accusation%20that%20has%20intensified%20the%20ongoing%20family%20feud%20over%20the%20late%20KK%20Modi's%20Rs%2011%2C000-crore%20inheritance%2C%20the%20Economic%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamir%20Modi%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Friday%2C%20alleging%20that%20his%20mother's%20personal%20security%20officer%20(PSO)%20and%20several%20directors%20of%20Godfrey%20Phillips%20caused%20him%20%26quot%3Bgrievous%20hurt%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20attempted%20to%20enter%20a%20scheduled%20board%20meeting%20at%20the%20company's%20Jasola%20office%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20Thursday%20when%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20scheduled%20board%20meeting%20of%20GP%20at%20Jasola%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20told%20The%20Economic%20Times.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20prevented%20by%20Bina%20Modi's%20PSO%20from%20entering%20the%20meeting.%20When%20I%20insisted%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20push%20me%20and%20said%20that%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20board%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confrontation%20resulted%20in%20him%20sustaining%20a%20broken%20index%20finger.%20Despite%20his%20injuries%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20attended%20the%20board%20meeting%20before%20seeking%20medical%20attention%2C%20reports%20CNBC-TV18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20index%20finger%20has%20been%20broken%20into%20two%20and%20requires%20a%20screw%20and%20wire%20to%20be%20put%20together%2C%20and%20I%20may%20not%20regain%20full%20function%20of%20my%20index%20finger%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20detailed%20in%20his%20complaint%20filed%20at%20Sarita%20Vihar%20police%20station.%20%26quot%3BThe%20screw%20used%20to%20fix%20the%20finger%20will%20stay%20with%20me%20for%20a%20lifetime%20and%20my%20right-hand%20index%20finger%20will%20never%20be%20wholly%20functional%2C%20I%20am%20informed%20by%20the%20medical%20practitioners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20imagined%20being%20assaulted%20in%20my%20own%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Samir%20Modi%20said%20from%20his%20New%20Friends%20Colony%20home%20in%20the%20capital.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20court%20case%20on%20settlement%20of%20shares%20is%20pending%2C%20I'll%20not%20sell%20my%20stake%20now.%20The%20effort%20is%20to%20remove%20me%20from%20the%20board%2C%20which%20will%20not%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamir%20Modi%20alleged%20he%20suspects%20the%20attack%20was%20premeditated%20to%20prevent%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20meeting%20and%20to%20pressure%20him%20into%20selling%20his%20stake.%20Despite%20a%20previous%20offer%20from%20his%20mother%20to%20buy%20his%20stake%20through%20a%20mediator%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20has%20now%20resolved%20not%20to%20agree%20to%20an%20exit%2C%20according%20to%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20feud%2C%20which%20has%20been%20ongoing%20since%20the%20death%20of%20KK%20Modi%2C%20involves%20a%20significant%20shareholding%20in%20Godfrey%20Phillips%20and%20other%20group%20companies.%20Samir%20Modi%20has%20also%20accused%20his%20mother%20of%20not%20distributing%20funds%20as%20stipulated%20in%20a%20trust%20deed%20executed%20by%20his%20father.%20This%20legal%20battle%20is%20currently%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20role%20at%20Godfrey%20Phillips%2C%20in%20which%20Phillip%20Morris%20holds%20a%2025%25%20share%2C%20Samir%20Modi%20also%20heads%20consumer%20businesses%20such%20as%20Colorbar%20Cosmetics%2C%2024%2F7%20Retail%2C%20and%20the%20direct%20selling%20platform%20Modicare.%20He%20claims%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20intended%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20fulfilling%20his%20duties%20as%20a%20director%2