0are%20Dhananjay%20Tapesingh%20alias%20Ajay%20Kashyap%2C%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20alias%20Nahvi%2C%20Vapsi%20Khan%20alias%20Waseem%20Chikna%2C%20and%20Rizwan%20Khan%2C%20each%20believed%20to%20have%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20plot.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20jail%2C%20his%20cousin%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20and%20associate%20Goldie%20Brar%2C%20allegedly%20facilitated%20the%20acquisition%20of%20the%20deadly%20weapons%20from%20the%20Pakistani%20dealer%20known%20only%20as%20Dogar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashyap%2C%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20lived%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai's%20Kalamboli.%20He%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20person%20identified%20as%20Sukha%20Shooter%2C%20who%20has%20Bishnoi's%20photo%20as%20his%20profile%20picture.%20Kashyap%20and%20his%20cohorts%20held%20clandestine%20meetings%20in%20strategic%20locations%20such%20as%20the%20Panvel%20bus%20stand%20and%20railway%20station%2C%20plotting%20to%20execute%20their%20plans%2C%20including%20reconnaissance%20of%20Salman%20Khan's%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20footprint%20extends%20across%20multiple%20states%20and%20borders%2C%20with%20Kashyap's%20trail%20leading%20to%20illegal%20arms%20depots%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Ganganagar%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Pakistan%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20between%20Kashyap%20and%20Bishnoi%20revealed%20frequent%20discussions%20among%20the%20associates%20about%20the%20exchange%20of%20weapons%20and%20coordination%20via%20WhatsApp%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20after%20assassinating%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20Bishnoi%20and%20Goldie%20Brar%20planned%20to%20pay%20a%20substantial%20sum%20of%20money%20to%20the%20hitmen%2C%20with%20the%20funds%20transferred%20from%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gang%20was%20prepared%20to%20use%20modern%20weapons%20such%20as%20AK-47s%2C%20M16s%2C%20and%20AK-92s%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20assassination.%20Similar%20weapons%20were%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moosewala.%20The%20gang%20members%20were%20shown%20weapons%20like%20AK-47s%20and%20ammunition%20through%20WhatsApp%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20attackers%20were%20instructed%20to%20flee%20to%20Kanyakumari%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20they%20would%20be%20ferried%20by%20sea%20to%20Sri%20Lanka.%20From%20there%2C%20arrangements%20were%20in%20place%20for%20their%20safe%20passage%20to%20another%20country%2C%20facilitated%20by%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20based%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigations%20uncovered%20the%20gang's%20collaboration%20with%20other%20criminal%20outfits%2C%20notably%20with%20the%20organisation%20formerly%20led%20by%20gangster%20Anand%20Pal%2C%20now%20overseen%20by%20his%20daughter%20Chinu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2014%2C%20when%20two%20bike-borne%20men%20opened%20fire%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra.%20After%20the%20incident%2C%20police%20arrested%20four%20suspects%3A%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%2C%20who%20were%20apprehended%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20while%20Anuj%20Thapan%20and%20another%20individual%20were%20detained%20in%20Punjab%20on%20April%2026.%20In%20total%2C%20six%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%20although%20Anuj%20Thapan%20died%20in%20police%20custody.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717227480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F67icvni8_salman-khan_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-guns-sri-lanka-escape-plan-how-salman-khan-murder-plot-was-hatched-5792555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AK-47%20and%20M-16%20rifles%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20minor%20sharpshooters%20and%20an%20escape%20plan%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20-%20the%20police%20have%20uncovered%20chilling%20details%20of%20an%20assassination%20plot%20to%20kill%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canon