a%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20voted%20to%20make%20the%20country%20stronger%2C%20and%20self-reliant.%20The%20way%20India%20has%20progressed%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20So%20not%20just%20us%2C%20but%20crores%20of%20people%20now%20see%20an%20India%20different%20from%20how%20it%20was%2010%20years%20ago%20and%20are%20hopeful%20about%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B10%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20had%20given%20up%20on%20politics%20and%20politicians.%20Now%20those%20people%20have%20placed%20their%20hopes%20on%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20are%20moving%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2063-year-old%20also%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20claims%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20would%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20when%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20PM%2C%20changed%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20themselves%20in%201976%20and%20were%20now%20trying%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20to%20divide%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20never%20works%20on%20a%20positive%20note.%20They%20never%20the%20country%20any%20positive%20message.%20They%20work%20with%20obstacle-creating%20powers%2C%20and%20always%20try%20to%20find%20issues%20that%20will%20divide%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20does%20not%20like%20when%20they%20see%20something%20that%20will%20unite%20the%20country%20and%20take%20it%20forward.%20Congress%20only%20wants%20to%20divide%20the%20society%20and%20keep%20playing%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20and%20is%20up%20against%20a%20united%20Opposition%2C%20who%20are%20contesting%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bl