the%20icy%20Himalayas%20at%20a%20staggering%20altitude%20of%2015%2C256%20feet.%20This%20village%20holds%20the%20distinction%20of%20hosting%20the%20highest%20polling%20station%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fngucqnfc_worlds-highest-polling-station-tashigang-pti_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20near%20the%20India-China%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20the%20Spiti%20valley%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Mandi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20one%20of%20the%20four%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20second%20largest%20in%20India.%20Bollywood%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20up%20against%20the%20Congress's%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polling%20station%20at%20Tashigang%2C%20serving%2062%20voters%20from%20Tashigang%20and%20Gete%2C%20has%20been%20made%20a%20model%20polling%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftrhjjrsg_worlds-highest-polling-station-tashigang-pti_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hour-and-a-half-long%20journey%20to%20Tashigang%2C%20located%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20a%20mountain%20facing%20the%20SDM's%20office%20in%20Kaza%2C%20is%20as%20formidable%20as%20the%20landscape%20itself%20--%20rugged%20terrain%2C%20narrow%20winding%20dirt%20roads%20and%20unpredictable%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20for%20Lal%20and%20his%20team%2C%20the%20assignment%20carries%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20In%20a%20place%20where%20the%20harsh%20environment%20shapes%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%2C%20facilitating%20the%20democratic%20process%20is%20both%20a%20%26quot%3Bduty%20and%20an%20honour%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20part%20of%20a%20team%20that%20conducted%20elections%20at%20Hikkim%20(also%20in%20the%20Spiti%20valley)%2C%20the%20second-highest%20polling%20station%20in%20the%20country%2C%20in%20the%20past.%20So%20I%20have%20some%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Lal%20said%2C%20laughing%20as%20he%20walked%20to%20board%20a%20white%20Bolero%20car%20with%20an%20electronic%20voting%20machine%20(EVM)%20in%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20pause%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EThoda%20dikkat%20toh%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(there%20will%20be%20some%20difficulties)%2C%26quot%3B%20acknowledging%20the%20challenges%20ahead%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20unaccustomed%20to%20such%20a%20difficult%20terrain%20with%20no%20mobile%20connectivity%20and%20limited%20power%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbbfn7klg_worlds-highest-polling-station-tashigang-pti_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20preparations%20are%20meticulous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20will%20get%20a%20satellite%20phone%20and%20runners%20will%20be%20deployed%20to%20relay%20polling%20data%20to%20the%20headquarters%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20District%20Commissioner%20Rahul%20Jain%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20terrain%20is%20tough%2C%20but%20our%20teams%20are%20committed%20and%20we%20have%20made%20all%20the%20preparations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20journey%20commenced%2C%20the%20paved%20road%20quickly%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20narrow%20and%20uneven%20dirt%20path.%20The%20brown%20hills%20on%20either%20side%20were%20dotted%20with%20white%20pools%20of%20snow%2C%20slowly%20melting%20in%20the%20sun.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20water%20from%20the%20melting%20snow%20accumulated%20on%20the%20dirt%20road%2C%20making%20it%20dangerous%20to%20drive%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20was%20breathtaking%20but%20completely%20desolate.%C2%94%20A%20few%20houses%20were%20visible%20only%20because%20of%20their%20bright%20colours%20against%20the%20brown%20hills.%20There%20is%20nothing%20for%20miles%20in%20between%2C%20and%20with%20no%20or%20very%20limited%20mobile%20connectivity%2C%20tourists%20frequently%20lose%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yellow-coloured%20polling%20station%20with%20the%20tricolour%20painted%20on%20its%20front%20is%20perched%20high%20on%20a%20hill%2C%20bleakly%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20barely%20any%20vegetation%2C%20barring%20wild%20grasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHighest%20polling%20station%20of%20India%2C%20Tashigang%20-%2072.%20Altitude%20-%204%2C650%20metres%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20message%20painted%20in%20blue%20and%20white%20on%20the%20front%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSwagatam.%20We%20heartily%20welcome%20all%20the%20voters%20to%20the%20world's%20highest%20polling%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20written%20in%20Hindi%20on%20the%20welcome%20board%2C%20adorned%20with%20colourful%20frills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reaching%20the%20polling%20station%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20police%20personnel%20accompanying%20the%20polling%20party%20stepped%20outside%20and%20tried%20calling%20home%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20there%20was%20no%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLag%20nahi%20raha%20hai%20(the%20call%20is%20not%20going%20through)%2C%26quot%3B%20Takor%20Mahtoji%20chuckled%2C%20tension%20replacing%20the%20smile%20on%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20have%20scaled%20such%20heights.%20Temperatures%20here%20are%20bone-chilling%20for%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20used%20to%20such%20cold%20conditions.%20I%20did%20not%20carry%20any%20warm%20clothes%20and%20bought%20new%20ones%20after%20reaching%20Kaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahtoji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20Prince%2C%20the%20micro-observer%20for%20elections%20at%20the%20Tashigang%20polling%20station%2C%20is%20a%20bank%20clerk%20from%20Bihar's%20Muzaffarpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTemperatures%20are%20reaching%2050%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Here%2C%20it%20is%20a%20different%20world.%20I%20hope%20everyone%20has%20got%20enough%20warm%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20special%20and%20important%20task%20we%20have%20been%20assigned.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20make%20people%20in%20inaccessible%20terrains%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20how%20can%20we%20tell%20the%20world%20that%20we%20are%20the%20strongest%20democracy%3F%26quot%3B%20Prince%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20temperatures%20in%20Tashigang%20range%20from%205%20to%2020%20degrees%20Celsius.%20But%20the%20mercury%20can%20drop%20due%20to%20sudden%20changes%20in%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2030%2C%20snowfall%20welcomed%20the%20polling%20party%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20with%20temperatures%20dropping%20to%20minus%205%20degrees%20Celsius%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinters%20are%20harsh%20and%20inhospitable%2C%20with%20temperatures%20dropping%20as%20low%20as%20minus%2035%20degrees%20Celsius.%20The%20hills%20remain%20buried%20in%20snow%20and%20the%20sole%20dirt%20road%20connecting%20Tashigang%20to%20Kaza%20is%20closed%2C%20confining%20families%20to%20their%20mud-and-brick%20homes%20for%20six%20months%2C%20said%20Tanzin%20Takpa%20(54)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Tashigang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pregnant%20woman%20had%20to%20be%20carried%20on%20a%20yak%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20Kaza%20at%20the%20time%20of%20delivery%20in%20February.%20She%20was%20lucky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20hospital%2C%20clinic%2C%20school%20or%20market%20in%20Tashigang.%20The%20residents%20travel%20to%20Kaza%2C%20around%2030%20kilometres%20away%2C%20for%20medical%20and%20other%20needs%2C%20Takpa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20oxygen%20concentration%20at%20high%20altitudes%20can%20lead%20to%20breathing%20issues.%20The%20icy-cold%20conditions%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20those%20arriving%20in%20higher%20hills.%20Adapting%20to%20the%20local%20environment%20could%20take%20days%2C%20if%20not%20weeks%2C%20said%20Kalzang%20Namgial%20(40).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fourth%20time%20that%20polling%20will%20be%20conducted%20at%20Tashigang%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20record%20books%20since%202019%20as%20the%20highest%20polling%20station%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20all%20the%20eligible%20voters%20exercised%20their%20franchise%20despite%20the%20immensely%20cold%20conditions%2C%20Jain%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pink-and-white%20tent%20has%20been%20pitched%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20polling%20station%20as%20a%20sitting%20area%20for%20the%20voters.%20The%20one-storied%20polling%20station%20has%20two%20rooms%20on%20each%20side%2C%20recently%20painted%20bright%20yellow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vehicle%20carried%20blankets%20and%20mattresses%20for%20the%20polling%20team%20and%20security%20personnel.%20Women%20working%20with%20the%20state's%20public%20works%20department%20helped%20unload%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20men%20and%20women%20PWD%20workers%20prepared%20tea%20and%20dinner%20for%20the%20polling%20team%20and%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20woman%20decorated%20the%20polling%20rooms%20with%20colourful%20balloons.%20She%20did%20not%20look%20like%20a%20local%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaira%20Raba%2C%20a%20tourist%20from%20Israel%2C%20travelled%20to%20Tashigang%20to%20volunteer.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20in%20India%20for%20a%20month.%20I%20came%20to%20the%20Spiti%20valley%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20where%20I%20got%20to%20know%20it%20houses%20the%20world's%20highest%20polling%20station.%20People%20told%20me%20it%20is%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20reach%20this%20place%20and%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20are%20very%20harsh.%20I%20could%20not%20miss%20seeing%20something%20so%20amazing.%20This%20is%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Raba%20told%20Press%20Trist%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanzom%20(18)%2C%20the%20youngest%20voter%20in%20the%20nearby%20Kee%20village%2C%20lent%20Raba%20a%20helping%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20the%20polling%20team%20facilitating%20the%20election%20process%20in%20such%20harsh%20climatic%20conditions%20strengthens%20one's%20trust%20in%20democracy.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20paved%20roads%20and%20permanent%20jobs%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20polling%20station%20that%20is%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20our%20opportunity%20to%20let%20the%20government%20know%20what%20we%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20selfie%20point%20has%20been%20set%20up%20outside%20against%20the%20brown%20of%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20blue%20of%20the%20skies.%20%26quot%3BMy%20vote%2C%20my%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says%2C%20capturing%20the%20spirit%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20remotest%20corner%20of%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717223340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ffp9f1rg4_worlds-highest-polling-station-tashigang-pti_625x300_01