f%20the%20teen%20accused%20of%20running%20over%20two%20people%20while%20driving%20the%20luxury%20car.%20The%20mother%20swapped%20her%20blood%20sample%20in%20order%20to%20prove%20that%20her%20son%20wasn't%20drunk%20when%20the%20accident%20occurred%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommissioner%20of%20Police%20Amitesh%20Kumar%20said%20the%20accident%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20minor's%20blood%20samples%20were%20replaced%20with%20those%20of%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20techies%20were%20killed%20on%20May%2019%20in%20Pune's%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20after%20a%20Porsche%20allegedly%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20drunk%20minor%20rammed%20into%20their%20two%20wheeler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%2017-year-old%20minor%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20an%20observation%20home%2C%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20kidnapping%20the%20family's%20driver%20and%20putting%20pressure%20on%20him%20to%20take%20the%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20revealed%20efforts%20by%20the%20influential%20family%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20crime.%20They%20first%20tried%20to%20convince%20their%20family%20driver%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20chilling%20crash%20in%20lieu%20of%20cash.%20When%20he%20denied%2C%20they%20kidnapped%20him%20and%20kept%20forcing%20him%20to%20confess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20irregularities%20in%20the%2017-year-old's%20medical%20examination%20at%20the%20state-run%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20had%20appointed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20Dr%20Pallavi%20Sapale%2C%20dean%20of%20Mumbai-based%20Grants%20Medical%20College%2C%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen's%20mother%20had%20earlier%20appeared%20in%20a%20video%20message%20in%20which%20she%20had%20said%20that%20a%20viral%20video%20purportedly%20featuring%20her%20son%20was%20fake.%20She%20had%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20police%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%26quot%3B%20her%20son%20and%20broke%20down%20on%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAneesh%20Awadhiya%20and%20Ashwini%20Kostha%2C%2024-year-old%20engineers%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20hit%20their%20bike%20late%20on%20May%2019.%20The%20teen%2C%20alleged%20to%20be%20driving%20the%20car%20drunk%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20on%20conditions%20widely%20described%20as%20flimsy%20--%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%2C%20told%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20cops%20for%2015%20days%20and%20seek%20treatment%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20outrage%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20modified%20its%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20an%20observation%20home%20till%20June%205%2C%20as%20a%20decision%20is%20taken%20on%20the%20police%20plea%20for%20permission%20to%20try%20the%20teen%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717219620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5q94mp9_mother-of-pune-teen-arrested_650x400_01_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmother-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-arrested-5791206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20latest%20development%20in%20the%20Pune%20Porsche%20crash%20case%2C%20Pune%20police%20have%20arrested%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20teen%20accused%20of%20running%20over%20two%20people%20while%20driving%20the%20luxury%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmother-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-arrested-5791206%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmother-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-arrested-5791206%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmother-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techi