0there%20are%20night%20landing%20restrictions%20at%20San%20Francisco%2C%20the%20sources%20said%20Air%20India%20officials%20have%20done%20the%20work%20for%20requisite%20permission%20to%20land%20there.%20The%20Delhi-San%20Francisco%20flight%20duration%20is%20around%2016%20hours%20and%20by%20the%20time%20it%20lands%20in%20the%20American%20city%2C%20it%20would%20be%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20take%20off%20at%20around%203.30%20pm%20on%20Thursday%2C%20was%20delayed%20for%20nearly%206%20hours%20before%20being%20rescheduled%20for%20Friday.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20flight%2C%20to%20be%20operated%20with%20a%20Boeing%20777%20aircraft%2C%20was%20first%20scheduled%20for%20around%2011%20am%20departure%20which%20was%20changed%20to%203%20pm%20and%20after%20finally%20pushing%20back%20at%20around%205.45%20pm%2C%20the%20plane%20came%20back%20to%20the%20bay%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20a%20technical%20glitch%20was%20suspected%20and%20later%20payload%20issues%20were%20noticed.%20The%20airline%20is%20expected%20to%20offload%20some%20cargo%20and%20then%20depart%20for%20San%20Francisco%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20sources%20said%20an%20announcement%20was%20made%20that%20due%20to%20temperature%20issues%2C%20the%20flight%20could%20not%20take%20off%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20air%20conditioning%20was%20also%20switched%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20statement%20from%20Air%20India%20on%20the%20inordinate%20flight%20delay%20while%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20aviation%20regulator%20DGCA%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20the%20airline%20for%20some%20flight%20delays%20and%20failure%20to%20take%20due%20care%20of%20the%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20show%20cause%20notice%2C%20the%20watchdog%20mentioned%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20of%20two%20international%20flights%20--%20AI%20183%20from%20Delhi%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20May%2030%20and%20AI%20179%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20May%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Air%20India's%20regular%20flight%20from%20Delhi%20to%20San%20Francisco%20departed%20at%20around%201900%20hours%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20some%20passengers%20of%20the%20Delhi-San%20Francisco%20flight%20had%20fainted%20as%20the%20aircraft's%20air-conditioning%20system%20was%20non-functional%20and%20passengers%20also%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20around%20an%20hour%20in%20the%20aerobridge%2C%20Shilpa%20Jain%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%2C%20who%20is%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20said%20that%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20changed%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20glitch%20and%20the%20passengers%20boarded%20another%20plane%2C%20wherein%20the%20air-conditioning%20system%20was%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20had%20aged%20people%20and%20children%2C%20who%20were%20feeling%20uneasy.%20Later%2C%20at%20around%202200%20hours%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20flight%20was%20rescheduled%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20the%20revised%20departure%20time%20was%20about%208%20pm%20and%20passengers%20had%20boarded%20the%20aircraft%20at%20around%207.20%20pm.%20With%20the%20air-conditioning%20system%20non-functional%2C%20passengers%20were%20agitated%20and%20after%20almost%20an%20hour%2C%20they%20came%20out.%20The%20passengers%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20in%20the%20aerobridge%20before%20the%20gates%20were%20opened%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20delay%20and%20subsequent%20rescheduling%20of%20the%20flight%20on%20Thursday%2C%20an%20Air%20India%20official%20said%20the%20aircraft%20had%20developed%20a%20technical%20issue%20and%20engineering%20checks%20were%20carried%20out.%20Due%20to%20the%20delay%2C%20the%20crew%20had%20crossed%20the%20Flight%20Duty%20Time%20Limitation%20(FDTL)%20and%20also%20if%20the%20flight%20had%20taken%20off%2C%20it%20would%20have%20reached%20San%20Francisco%20when%20there%20are%20night%20landing%20restrictions%20there%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20the%20flight%20was%20originally%20rescheduled%20for%2011%20am%20departure%20on%20Friday%20and%20that%20has%20now%20been%20revised%20to%203%20pm.%20She%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20airline%20did%20not%20offer%20the%20option%20to%20reschedule%20or%20cancel%20the%20bookings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20airline%20official%20claimed%20that%20passengers%20were%20offered%20the%20options%20of%20full%20refund%2C%20complimentary%20rescheduling%20and%20hotel%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20one%20week%20that%20Air%20India%20passengers%20on%20a%20San%20Francisco%20flight%20have%20faced%20a%20harrowing%20time%20due%20to%20inordinate%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20some%20passengers%20of%20the%20AI%20183%20flight%20took%20to%20social%20media%20complaining%20about%20the%20delay%20and%20one%20of%20them%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20air-conditioning%20in%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20privatisation%20story%20that%20has%20failed%20it%20is%20%40airindia%20%40DGCAIndia%20AI%20183%20flight%20has%20been%20delayed%20for%20over%208%20hours%2C%20passengers%20were%20made%20to%20board%20the%20plane%20without%20air%20conditioning%2C%20and%20then%20deplaned%20after%20some%20people%20fainted%20in%20the%20flight.%20This%20is%20inhuman!%20%40JM_Scindia%2C%26quot%3B%20Shweta%20Punj%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20passengers%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20take%20off%20at%204%20pm%20on%20May%2024%2C%20was%20rescheduled%20and%20finally%20departed%20at%20around%205.30%20pm%20on%20May%2025.%20The%20inordinate%20delay%20was%20due%20to%20multiple%20reasons%2C%20including%20a%20technical%20glitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717219200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fafkgb5tg_air-india-flight-delhi-airport_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flight-to-san-francisco-takes-off-after-30-hour-delay-in-delhi-5789283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20200%20passengers%20of%20a%20San%20Francisco-bound%20Air%20India%20flight%20faced%20an%20ordeal%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20due%20to%20a%20delay%20of%20over%2030%20hours%20caused%20by%20a%20technical%20glitch%2C%20the%20aircraft's%20non-functional%20air%20conditioning%20system%20and%20payload%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flight-to-san-francisco-takes-off-after-30-hour-delay-in-delhi-5789283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flight-to-san-francisco-takes-off-after-30-hour-delay-in-delhi-5789283%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flight-to-san-francisco-takes-off-after-30-hour-delay-in-delhi-5789283%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fit%20To%20Play%20%26quot%3BFor%203%20Years%26quot%3B%2C%20Karthik%20Reveals%20Real%20Reason%20Behind%20Retirement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dinesh%20Karthik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F666-dinesh-karthik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDinesh%20Karthik%3C%2Fa%3E%20retired%20from%20the%20Indian%20Premier