act%20that%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20for%20him%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20also%20contributed%20to%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20big%20believer%20of%20whatever%20I%20look%20to%20do%2C%20I%20try%20to%20give%20it%20100%25%20commitment%20and%20do%20whatever%20I%20can%20to%20be%20the%20best%20in%20that.%20And%20I%20thought%20from%20hereon%20for%20me%20to%20play%20X%20amount%20of%20matches%20is%20going%20to%20be%20hard.%20Mentally%20pushing%20myself%20for%20so%20long%20in%20terms%20of%20doing%20everything%20in%20the%20lead-up%2C%20even%20if%20I%20falter%20a%20little%20bit%20I%20wouldn't%20be...%20even%20though%20from%20the%20outside%20people%20wouldn't%20know%2C%20but%20internally%20I%20would%20find%20it%20very%20hard%20and%20I%20would%20be%20living%20with%20guilt.%20I%20don't%20want%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20all%20that%20into%20account%2C%20I%20thought%20this%20is%20the%20time%20%5Bto%20retire%5D.%20And%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20I%20do%2C%20I%20cannot%20play%20for%20India%20again%20was%20very%20evident.%20So%20it%20was%20the%20last%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717218240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fus6k3a28_dinesh-karthik-ipl-retirement_625x300_23_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffit-to-play-another-3-years-dinesh-karthik-reveals-real-reason-behind-retirement-5778987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dinesh%20Karthik%20retired%20from%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20following%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru's%20exit%20from%20the%20competition%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffit-to-play-another-3-years-dinesh-karthik-reveals-real-reason-behind-retirement-5778987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3