ired%20to%20strike%20Mr%20Khan's%20car%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Panvel%2C%20armed%20with%20weapons%20sourced%20from%20a%20Pakistani%20arms%20supplier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20and%20arrested%20four%20individuals%20linked%20to%20this%20conspiracy.%20This%20follows%20an%20incident%20on%20April%2014%2C%20when%20two%20bike-borne%20men%20opened%20fire%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20alongside%20his%20Canada-based%20cousin%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20associate%20Goldie%20Brar%2C%20had%20reportedly%20acquired%20AK-47s%2C%20M-16s%2C%20and%20other%20high-calibre%20weapons%20from%20a%20Pakistani%20arms%20dealer.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20either%20ambush%20Mr%20Khan's%20vehicle%20or%20attack%20his%20farmhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20firing%20incident%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20Bandra%20residence%2C%20police%20arrested%20four%20suspects%3A%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%20were%20apprehended%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20while%20Anuj%20Thapan%20and%20another%20individual%20were%20detained%20in%20Punjab%20on%20April%2026.%20In%20total%2C%20six%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%20although%20Anuj%20Thapan%20died%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circumstances%20of%20Thapan's%20death%20have%20drawn%20significant%20scrutiny.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20expressed%20frustration%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bincomplete%26quot%3B%20autopsy%20report%20presented%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20lacked%20vital%20details%2C%20such%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiagram%20of%20the%20ligature%20mark%26quot%3B%20found%20on%20Thapan's%20neck%20and%20information%20on%20any%20other%20potential%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThapan's%20mother%2C%20Rita%20Devi%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20on%20May%203%2C%20alleging%20that%20her%20son%20was%20physically%20assaulted%20and%20tortured%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death%20on%20May%201%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20crime%20branch%20lock-up.%20While%20the%20police%20maintain%20that%20Thapan%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20Ms%20Devi's%20petition%20calls%20for%20a%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20probe%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717217820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjqh9bdug_salman-khan-_625x300_01_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-ak-47s-from-pak-bishnoi-gang-plotted-salman-khan-murder-plan-sources-5791502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20uncovered%20yet%20another%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-ak-47s-from-pak-bishnoi-gang-plotted-salman-khan-murder-plan-sources-5791502%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-ak-47s-from-pak-bishnoi-gang-plotted-salman-khan-murder-plan-sources-5791502%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-ak-47s-from-pak-bishnoi-gang-plotted-salman-khan-murder-plan-sources-5791502%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226-Month-Old%20US%20Boy%20Dies%20After%20Pet%20Husky%20Attacks%20Him%20In%20Crib%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%206-week-old%20baby%20was%20mauled%20to%20death%20by%20the%20family's%20dog%20while%20sleeping%20in%20his%20crib%20in%20US'%20Tennessee.%20Ezra%20Mansoor%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20seemingly%20tame%20husky%20that%20has%20been%20living%20with%20the%20family%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELittle%20Ezra%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20on%20Thursday%2C%20six%20days%20after%20the%20unexpected%20attack.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20critical%20condition%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20suffering%20from%20a%20brain%20bleed