igh%20Court%20Orders%20Expanded%20Probe%20into%20Nursing%20Colleges%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20an%20expanded%20and%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20the%20recognition%20practices%20of%20nursing%20colleges%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20decision%20came%20following%20multiple%20applications%20seeking%20modifications%20to%20a%20previous%20court%20order%20dated%20September%2028%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20court%20had%20ordered%20a%20comprehensive%20CBI%20inquiry%20into%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Indian%20Nursing%20Council%2C%20MP%20Medical%20Science%20University%2C%20and%20MP%20Nursing%20Council%20up%20to%20the%20year%202017.%20However%2C%20modifications%20were%20deemed%20necessary%20after%20it%20was%20highlighted%20that%20the%20MP%20Nursing%20Council%20was%20constituted%20only%20in%202018.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20court%20has%20extended%20the%20inquiry%20period%20to%20include%20the%202020-21%20academic%20session%20to%20ensure%20thoroughness%20and%20accuracy%20in%20the%20investigation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adjustment%20aims%20to%20eliminate%20any%20confusion%20and%20to%20ensure%20a%20meticulous%20examination%20of%20the%20recognition%20processes%20of%20nursing%20colleges%2C%20particularly%20those%20that%20closed%20mid-session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20in%20addressing%20concerns%20related%20to%20student%20enrollment%20in%20nursing%20colleges%2C%20the%20court%20clarified%20that%20students%20from%20deficient%20colleges%20should%20be%20permitted%20to%20participate%20in%20examinations%20for%20the%202020-21%20session.%20Enrollment%20for%20subsequent%20sessions%20will%20be%20considered%20once%20exams%20for%20those%20sessions%20are%20scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasizing%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20practical%20training%20in%20nursing%20education%2C%20the%20court%20has%20also%20ordered%20a%20reinspection%20of%20169%20colleges%20previously%20cleared%20by%20the%20CBI.%20This%20decision%20comes%20amid%20serious%20allegations%20of%20bribery%20involving%20CBI%20officials%20who%20were%20found%20accepting%20bribes%20from%20some%20colleges%20in%20exchange%20for%20favorable%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20reinspection%20process%2C%20the%20court%20has%20mandated%20that%20CBI%20teams%20be%20accompanied%20by%20district%20court%20registrars%20authorized%20by%20the%20Principal%20District%20Judge%20of%20the%20respective%20districts.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20inspections%20will%20be%20videographed%20to%20maintain%20transparency%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20significant%20move%2C%20the%20court%20has%20appointed%20a%20committee%20under%20Retired%20Justice%20Shri%20RK%20Shrivastava%20to%20oversee%20the%20standards%20of%20practical%20training%20in%20nursing%20education.%20This%20committee%20is%20tasked%20with%20examining%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20practical%20training%2C%20from%20hospital%20linkages%20for%20practical%20training%20to%20the%20assessment%20of%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20directed%20that%20the%20reinspections%20commence%20immediately%20and%20be%20completed%20within%20three%20months%20to%20expedite%20the%20investigative%20process%20and%20ensure%20timely%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20State%20Government%20to%20reconsider%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20Administrator%20in%20the%20MP%20Nursing%20Council%20following%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20qualifications%20of%20the%20current%20appointee.%20The%20petitioner%20sought%20relief%20for%20the%20State%20Government%20to%20evaluate%20the%20qualifications%20of%20the%20appointed%20Administrator%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20per%20a%20prior%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717214280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjgoglet_mp-nurs