%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20also%20seemed%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20a%20host%20of%20big%20Australian%20names%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20IPL%20coaches%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Fleming%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F187-stephen-fleming-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStephen%20Fleming%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andy%20Flower%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F189-andy-flower-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndy%20Flower%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20the%20role%20of%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20but%20it's%20Gambhir%20who%20seems%20to%20be%20ahead%20of%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir's%20name%20started%20getting%20discussed%20as%20KKR%20produced%20an%20emphatic%20performance%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20finishing%20as%20the%20No.%201%20side.%20A%20few%20games%20later%2C%20the%20Knight%20Riders%20defeated%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%20the%20final%20to%20take%20the%20title%20home.%20After%20the%20final%2C%20Gambhir%20also%20had%20a%20lengthy%20chat%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah.%20Though%20the%20content%20of%20the%20chat%20isn't%20known%2C%20the%20visals%20did%20fuel%20speculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fgautam-gambhir-india-cricket-team-head-coach-bcci-kkr-mentor-role-2546422-2024-05-31%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gambhir%20is%20now%20set%20to%20replace%20Dravid%20as%20Team%20India's%20head%20coach.%20Though%20Gambhir%20recently%20took%20the%20role%20of%20KKR's%20mentor%2C%20leaving%20his%20job%20with%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%2C%20another%20IPL%20side%20he%20had%20joined%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20coaching%20staff%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20doesn't%20have%20any%20experience%20of%20being%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20a%20national%20side%2C%20or%20even%20IPL%2C%20his%20role%20in%20taking%20KKR%20to%20IPL%20triumph%20this%20year%20was%20reportedly%20enough%20for%20the%20BCCI%20to%20seriously%20consider%20his%20name%20as%20Dravid's%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20invited%20applications%20for%20the%20head%20coach's%20role%20by%20May%2027%2C%20and%20is%20said%20to%20have%20received%20over%203000%20forms%2C%20including%20some%20fake%20'Sachin%20Tendulkars'%2C%20'Narendra%20Modis'%20and%20'Amit%20Shahs'.%20The%20board%20is%20likely%20to%20being%20the%20process%20of%20interviewing%20shortlisted%20candidates%20soon%2C%20with%20the%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Committee%20leading%20that%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717213020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ff7h3h71o_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-set-to-replace-rahul-dravid-as-india-head-coach-report-5791281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20reportedly%20ready%20to%20take%20up%20the%20role%20of%20Team%20India's%20head%20coach%2C%20replacing%20Rahul%20Dravid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-set-to-replace-rahul-dravid-as-india-head-coach-report-5791281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-set-to-replace-rahul-dravid-as-india-head-coach-report-5791281%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-set-to-replace-rahul-dravid-as-india-head-coach-report-5791281%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Fire%20At%20Delhi's%20Kashmere%20Gate%20Police%20Station%2C%20Documents%20Destroyed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Kashmere%20Gate%20Metro%20police%20station%20in%20Delhi%20burst%20into%20flames%20last%20night%2C%20leaving%20the%20facility%20in%20ruins.%2