C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20especially%20true%20if%20you%20have%20more%20than%20one%20phone%20number%2C%20such%20as%20a%20cell%20number%2C%20a%20work%20number%2C%20and%20a%20home%20landline.%20Google%20Voice%20can%20streamline%20your%20calls%20and%20texts%2C%20helping%20ensure%20you%20never%20miss%20an%20important%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Voice%20has%20a%20fascinating%20history%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20major%20spat%20between%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Eric%20Schmidt%20and%20the%20late%20Apple%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteve%20Jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20sought%20to%20bring%20Google%20Voice%20to%20the%20iPhone%20as%20an%20app%2C%20but%20Apple%20rejected%20the%20move%20amid%20Google's%20growing%20forays%20into%20the%20telecommunications%20market.%20The%20tensions%20culminated%20with%20Schmidt's%20resignation%20from%20Apple's%20board%20of%20directors%20in%202009.%20Apple%20ultimately%20relented%2C%20adding%20Google%20Voice%20to%20the%20App%20Store%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20controversy%20around%20Google%20Voice%20continues%20today%3A%20in%202024%2C%20a%20federal%20jury%20ordered%20Google%20to%20pay%20%2412%20million%20in%20damages%20for%20infringing%20on%20internet%20voice-calling%20patents%20with%20Google%20Voice.%20It's%20one%20of%20several%20major%20federal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20faced%20throughout%202023%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22740644a9-2a21-4240-82db-d1cf4ed0e79f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20would%20someone%20use%20a%C2%A0Google%C2%A0Voice%C2%A0number%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Voice%20allows%20you%20to%20combine%20all%20your%20phone%20services%20and%20forward%20calls%20to%20several%20devices%20at%20a%20time.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20landline%20at%20home%2C%20a%20business%20phone%2C%20and%20your%20personal%20smartphone%2C%20rather%20than%20bouncing%20people%20between%20three%20different%20numbers%20and%20devices%2C%20you%20can%20give%20out%20one%20simple%20Google%20Voice%20number.%20When%20someone%20calls%2C%20you'll%20be%20notified%20at%20all%20three%20numbers%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20Google%20Voice%20on%20a%20computer%20to%20place%20and%20receive%20calls.%20But%20before%20you%20can%20use%20any%20of%20Google%20Voice's%20features%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%C2%A0have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fcreate-gmail-account%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0first.%20As%20noted%2C%20you'll%20also%20need%20to%20have%20an%20existing%20US-based%20mobile%20or%20landline%20phone%20number%2C%20so%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20Google%20Voice%20is%20not%20a%20free%20phone%20service%20but%20rather%20an%20add-on%20to%20your%20extant%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20users%20who%20simply%20have%20too%20many%20phones%20and%20numbers%20to%20manage%2C%20Google%20Voice%20is%20a%20great%20resource%20for%20merging%20multiple%20communication%20channels.%20It's%20also%20good%20for%20regular%20travelers%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20bounce%20between%20carriers%20because%20you%20can%20use%20your%20Google%20Voice%20number%20internationally.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20not%20work%20in%20all%20countries%2C%20and%20rates%20vary%20by%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20find%20yourself%20changing%20phone%20numbers%20and%20paying%20a%20fortune%20for%20international%20calls%2C%20or%C2%A0for%20those%20users%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-record-a-phone-call-on-iphone-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20incom