ractice-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-way%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Google%20Flights%20search%20for%20about%20six%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20it%20costs%20about%20%24700%20with%20the%20multi-city%20tool%20to%20fly%20from%20NYC%20to%20Rome%20and%20then%20from%20Barcelona%20back%20to%20NYC.%20But%20with%20the%20one-way%20tool%2C%20it's%20nearly%20%241%2C000.%20And%20a%20train%20from%20Rome%20to%20Barcelona%20may%20cost%20around%20%2480%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raileurope.com%2Fen-us%2Fdestinations%2Frome-barcelona-train%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Rail%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20open-jaw%20flights%20would%20save%20%24220.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Google%20Flights%20search%20using%20the%20multi-city%20tool%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665a2bd51cd3b1779042400a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20a%20multi-city%20search%20on%20Google%20Flights.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Flights%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20savings%20can%20be%20even%20greater.%20In%20another%20search%20in%20the%20same%20timeframe%2C%20flying%20from%20Indianapolis%20to%20Paris%20and%20then%20from%20Madrid%20back%20to%20Indianapolis%20would%20cost%20about%20%24930%20with%20the%20multi-city%20tool%20and%20%241%2C600%20with%20the%20one-way%20tool.%20Factor%20in%20a%20%2465%20train%20ticket%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raileurope.com%2Fen-us%2Fdestinations%2Fparis-madrid-train%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Rail%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20you'd%20save%20about%20%24600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20that%20these%20prices%20reflect%20just%20one%20person%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20families%20can%20save%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22681f1081-7973-4fe1-a461-e57034730e18%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%