2Mastercard's%20AI%20system%20is%20helping%20banks%20keep%20fraudsters%20in%20check%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20could%20save%20millions%20of%20dollars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20person%20pays%20for%20a%20transaction%20on%20their%20phone%20with%20a%20digital%20Mastercard%20credit%20card%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66593c1fcc442a2f676c9539%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMastercard%2C%20an%20international%20card-payment-services%20company%2C%20interacts%20with%20banks%20worldwide.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20company%20has%20used%20AI%20to%20try%20to%20identify%20when%20customers%20may%20be%20about%20to%20be%20defrauded.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcxo-ai-playbook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECXO%C2%A0AI%C2%A0Playbook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20straight%20talk%20from%20business%20leaders%20on%20how%20they're%20testing%20and%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20%26quot%3BCXO%20AI%20Playbook%2C%26quot%3B%20Business%20Insider%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20mini%20case%20studies%20about%20AI%20adoption%20across%20industries%2C%20company%20sizes%2C%20and%20technology%20DNA.%20We've%20asked%20each%20of%20the%20featured%20companies%20to%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20problems%20they're%20trying%20to%20solve%20with%20AI%2C%20who's%20making%20these%20decisions%20internally%2C%20and%20their%20vision%20for%20using%20AI%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%201966%2C%20Mastercard%20has%20been%20a%20provider%20of%20payment-card%20services%20to%20the%20world's%20biggest%20banks%20and%20millions%20of%20consumers.%20The%20company%20is%20adapting%20to%20the%20constantly%20evolving%20threats%20scammers%20and%20criminals%20pose%20to%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec04abf8-6dc5-4015-93f4-02f9ad5ed95c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20analysis%3A%20What%20problem%20was%20the%20company%20trying%20to%20solve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20decades%2C%20payment%20fraud%20used%20to%20be%20people%20using%20your%20card%20details%20that%20they'd%20either%20bought%2C%20found%2C%20or%20counterfeited%2C%20either%20in%20person%20or%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Reid%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20identity%20solutions%20at%20Mastercard%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20trends%20in%20payment%20fraud%20have%20changed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20banks%20and%20card%20providers%20have%20to%20keep%20up.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20new%20trends%20in%20fraud%2C%20Reid%20said%2C%20is%20what's%20known%20as%20authorized-push-payment%20fraud%2C%20where%20a%20scammer%20persuades%20someone%20to%20send%20them%20money%20by%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20reliable%20figure%2C%20such%20as%20a%20bank%2C%20public%20authority%2C%20or%20romantic%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20when%20a%20card%20user%20is%20about%20to%20send%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20%E2%80%94%20and%20lose%20it%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20scammer%20is%20tricky%2C%20Reid%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20detect%20you%20are%20a%20victim%20or%20about%20to%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20crime%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%20The%20company%20believes%20artificial%20intelligence%20can%20help%20identify%20when%20that%20fraud%20is%20about%20to%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3cf2d12-27c1-409c-b92f-616d9a187a34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20an%20AI%20fraud-detection%20system%20began%20as%20a%20pilot%20program%20in%20the%20UK.%20At%20Mastercard%2C%20the%20teams%20working%20on%20the%20project%20included%20Reid's%20identity%20group%2C%20the%20security%20and%20cyberinnovation%20team%2C%20and%20the%20open-banking%20team%2C%20which%20works%20on%20connecting%20competing%20banks%20with%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221951%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chris%20reid%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665937c8d0b8e1c832ca9dd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Reid%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20identity%20solutions%20at%20Mastercard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Chris%20Reid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20said%20he%20believed%20the%20work%20couldn't%20have%20been%20done%20without%20buy-in%20from%20banks%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20including%20Lloyds%20Bank%2C%20NatWest%2C%20and%20TSB%20Bank%2C%20which%20put%20aside%20their%20rivalries%20to%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20only%20works%20when%20we%20all%20come%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20nice%20thing%20we%20see%20around%20fraud%20and%20security%20is%2C%20every%20day%2C%20the%20banks%20are%20competing%20to%20win.%20On%20fraud%20and%20security%2C%20we're%20all%20competing%20to%20beat%20fraudsters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd30701-463a-4b66-b855-30c65acda283%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20those%20banks%2C%20the%20teams%20at%20Mastercard%20began%20developing%20an%20AI%20system%20to%20identify%20signs%20in%20the%20accounts%20of%20both%20victims%20and%20scammers%20that%20someone%20was%20about%20to%20be%20defrauded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20give%20our%20bank%20customers%20a%20three-dimensional%20view%20of%20the%20two%20accounts%20in%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard's%20AI%20system%20is%20trained%20on%20data%20from%20both%20legitimate%20and%20fraudulent%20payment%20activities.%20Using%20this%20information%2C%20it%20monitors%20and%20identifies%20suspicious%20transaction%20behaviors%20and%20looks%20at%20data%2C%20such%20as%20payee%20names%2C%20to%20identify%20suspect%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20look%20at%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20relationships%20linked%20to%20a%20fraudster's%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrime%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20the%20legitimate%20financial%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20tend%20to%20find%20funds%20flow%20out%20into%20various%20mule%20or%20drop%20accounts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20provides%20an%20AI-powered%20risk%20score%20for%20transactions%20and%20accounts%20in%20real%20time%2C%20alerting%20the%20banks%20if%20Mastercard%20suspects%20a%20payment%20is%20being%20made%20to%20a%20known%20fraudster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220de6e3ad-c6e8-47ff-8ec6-6585acb0a367%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20said%20TSB%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20really%20transparent%20in%20helping%20us%20understand%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20fraud%20prevented%20among%20TSB's%20customers%2C%20if%20it%20was%20extrapolated%20across%20the%20UK%20banking%20sector%2C%20%26quot%3Beverything%20else%20being%20equal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AI%20system%20would%20save%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ean%20estimated%20%C2%A3100%20million%2C%20or%20%24126%20million%2C%20in%20the%20UK%20alone%2C%20Reid%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Mastercard's%20tech%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20good%26quot%3B%20at%20identifying%20%26quot%3Bimpersonation%20scams%2C%20romance%20scams%2C%20and%20purchase%20scams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b10d7e8-3d1f-4e76-a240-334aa7a6ce4a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard%20needs%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20scammers%2C%20Reid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFraud%20is%20an%20incredibly%20successful%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BFraudsters%20are%20investing%20in%20product%20development%20and%20their%20own%20efficiency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20reason%2C%20Mastercard%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20AI%20systems.%20Currently%2C%20the%20system%20provides%20an%20AI-identified%20risk%20score%20for%20the%20potential%20victim's%20account.%20By%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20Mastercard%20wants%20to%20provide%20a%20risk%20score%20for%20scamming%20suspects%20to%20try%20to%20raise%20awareness%20among%20banks%20about%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20doubles%20the%20ability%20for%20us%20to%20stop%20the%20money%20getting%20to%20the%20criminals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20tell%20the%20scammer's%20bank%2C%20'This%20is%20a%20high-risk%20transaction%3B%20you%20might%20want%20to%20delay%20releasing%20the%20funds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard%20is%20also%20working%20to%20create%20more%20practical%20applications%20for%20the%20risk%20score%2C%20which%20is%20useful%20to%20banks%20at%20a%20high%20level%20but%20perhaps%20not%20for%20rank-and-file%20bank%20employees%20tasked%20with%20supporting%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContact-center%20agents%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20are%20trained%20and%20knowledgeable%20in%20fraud%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20turn%20the%20score%20into%20something%20that's%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20working%20to%20be%20able%20to%20ultimately%20stop%20that%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20If%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20sharing%20your%20company's%20AI%20journey%2C%20email%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajhood%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejhood%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22defau