chemical%20insecticides.%20I%20never%20knew%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20we%20were%20causing%20ourselves%20and%20to%20those%20buying%20crops%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2057-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20inorganic%20farming%20a%20sin%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20convert%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20(1.4%20acre)%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20training%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20growing%20crops%20on%20a%20small%20part%20of%20our%20land%20using%20natural%20farming%2C%20but%20later%2C%20I%20swore%20never%20to%20use%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20the%20field%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%3C%2Ffigc