.%20He%20hopes%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20consultation%20service%20with%20an%20annual%20maintenance%20contract%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20water%20filter%20companies%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20working%20model%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288886%2Fsustainable-farmhouse-in-gujarat-gets-zero-power-bills-recycles-greywater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreywater%20recycling%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20two%20school%20projects%2C%20Prashant%20borrowed%20money%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20build%20the%20solutions.%20He%20is%20now%20working%20with%20village%20administrations%20and%20the%20ashram%20on%20a%20revenue-based%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20people%20can%20pay%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20a%20small%20fee.%20We%20want%20to%20generate%20revenue%20instead%20of%20depending%20on%20funds%20from%20larger%20players%20as%20this%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20fund%20initiatives%20in%20villages%20and%20communities%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20though%2C%20he%20is%20managing%20as%20his%20wife%20has%20a%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20keeps%20him%20going%20is%20the%20response%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20has%20been%20very%20positive%20everywhere%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been.%20Right%20from%20villages%20to%20cities%2C%20people%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20stagnant%20water%20and%20want%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20this%20water%20conservationist%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20living%20has%20to%20be%20more%20than%20making%20money%2C%20it%20has%20to%20involve%20fulfilling%20the%20needs%20of%20people%20who%20are%20within%20your%20sphere%20of%20influence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20email%20Prashant%20on%20