-7-1716443197-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-7-1716443197-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-7-1716443197-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-7-1716443197-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20farmers%20of%20Ladakh%20now%20have%20access%20to%20oil%2C%20water%20and%20better%20policies%20because%20of%20Upadhyaya%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20thus%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20sun%20drying%2C%20optimising%20the%20hygiene%20quotient%20and%20teaching%20the%20locals%20to%20market%20the%20fruit%20to%20customers%20using%20words%20like%20%E2%80%98organic%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98solar%20dried%E2%80%99.%20Currently%2C%20the%20fruit%20retails%20for%20Rs%20465.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20nudged%20the%20women%20farmers%20to%20explore%20other%20crops%2C%20like%20soybeans%20and%20oyster%20mushrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20saw%20these%20alternatives%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205675%2Findia-women-anaemia-iron-deficiency-symptom-causes-treatment-doctor-low-haemoglobin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepidemic%20of%20anaemia%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20grapples%20the%20Ladakh%20region.%20Through%20these%20initiatives%2C%20Takmachik%20became%20an%20eco-village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20first%20eco-village%20of%20Ladakh%20was%20seeing%20results%20with%20its%20eco-friendly%20practices%2C%20Upadhyaya%20was%20flooded%20with%20requests%20to%20replicate%20the%20model%20in%20the%20other%20villages%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA