3A%22%3Cp%3ESeveral%20urban%20gardeners%20opt%20to%20save%20seeds%20as%20it%20allows%20them%20to%20cultivate%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20of%20consistent%20quality%20in%20the%20next%20season%20and%20of%20course%2C%20save%20money%20and%20become%20self-reliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurat-based%20home%20gardener%20Anupama%20Desai%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20know%20the%20quality%2C%20age%2C%20or%20if%20there%20is%20any%20kind%20of%20chemical%20coating%20on%20seeds%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Once%20purchased%2C%20you%20cannot%20return%20them.%20So%20it%20is%20better%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estore%20seeds%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20your%20garden%2C%20as%20there%20is%20no%20compromise%20on%20their%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2014%20years%2C%20she%20has%20been%20growing%20seasonal%20vegetables%20and%20has%20been%20collecting%20seeds%20of%20most%20of%20the%20produce%20grown%20at%20home.%20%E2%80%9CBelieve%20me%2C%20storing%20seeds%20at%20home%20makes%20your%20gardening%20work%20very%20easy.%20It%20does%20not%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2056-year-old%20gardener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Anupama%20shares%2010%20easy%20tips%20to%20store%20seeds%20in%20summer%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20them%20in%20the%20next%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20store%20seeds%20of%20watermelon%2C%20muskmelon%2C%20%3Cem%3Egalka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sponge%20gourd)%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20%3Cem%3Evalor%20papdi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(field%20beans)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekakdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Armenian%20cucumber)%2C%20etc%20in%20this%20season%20(May-end).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20watermelon%20and%20muskmelon%20are%20fruit%20plants%20and%20can%20easily%20be%20grown%20on%20terraces.%20After%20cleaning%20the%20seeds%2C%20let%20them%20dry%20on%20tissue%20paper.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%20the%20vegetables%20like%20cucumber%2C%20ridge%20gourd%2C%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20different%20types%20of%20beans%20dry%20on%20the%20plant%20instead%20of%20plucking%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20scooping%20out%20seeds%2C%20keep%20them%20in%20a%20clean%20and%20airtight%20plastic%20or%20glass%20container.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350675%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20scooping%20out%20seeds%2C%20keep%20them%20in%20a%20clean%20and%20airtight%20plastic%20or%20glass%20container.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWait%20until%20vegetables%20dry%20up%20and%20change%20their%20colour%20to%20brown.%20You%20can%20scoop%20out%20the%20seeds%20at%20that%20stage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoid%20storing%20seeds%20from%20the%20vegetables%20bought%20in%20the%20marke